a-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"A screenshot of the game library in the EA App.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"A screenshot of the game library in the EA App.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/66b023149db7076872bcea2c0740a8a0.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/66b023149db7076872bcea2c0740a8a0.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/66b023149db7076872bcea2c0740a8a0.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"A screenshot of the game library in the EA App.\" data-chomp-id=\"66b023149db7076872bcea2c0740a8a0\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"756\" data-alt=\"A screenshot of the game library in the EA App.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/66b023149db7076872bcea2c0740a8a0.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: EA / Kotaku\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"66b023149db7076872bcea2c0740a8a0\" data-recommend-id=\"image://66b023149db7076872bcea2c0740a8a0\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1343\" data-height=\"756\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"A screenshot of the game library in the EA App.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eEA’s Origin app has always topped the charts of things no one wants to have, alongside venereal diseases. \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-