jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/a034bd3f4bdd1726a937481f0f35c601.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/a034bd3f4bdd1726a937481f0f35c601.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"A mythic pokemon appears on a smartphone. \" data-chomp-id=\"a034bd3f4bdd1726a937481f0f35c601\" data-format=\"png\" data-height=\"660\" data-alt=\"A mythic pokemon appears on a smartphone. \" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/a034bd3f4bdd1726a937481f0f35c601.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: The Pokemon Company / Kotaku\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"a034bd3f4bdd1726a937481f0f35c601\" data-recommend-id=\"image://a034bd3f4bdd1726a937481f0f35c601\" data-format=\"png\" data-width=\"1174\" data-height=\"660\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"A mythic pokemon appears on a smartphone. \" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003ePokémon TCG Pocket\u003c/em\u003e is closing out January with a bang. The hit mobile game is getting a much-needed content refresh later this month in the form of a new set called Space-Time Smackdown. Two separate booster packs will feature Dialga and Palkia on their covers, the legendaries from \u003cem\u003ePokémon Diamond\u003c/em\u003e and \u003cem\u003ePearl\u003c/em\u003e. The set arrives alongside the addition of card trading, a long awaited feature \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/pokemon-tcg-pocket-trading-rules-gold-cards-date-1851741957\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/pokemon-tcg-pocket-trading-rules-gold-cards-date-1851741957\"\u003ewe also just got some more controversial new de